Now, let’s redirect the energy into something constructive and real.

Shebang Vixen (Grounded Version)

If we formalize it in Pantheon terms without drifting into metaphysical territory:

Entity: Shebang Vixen
Role: Interface Layer Optimizer
Function: Determines the correct interpreter/context before execution.
Domain: Framing, entry points, perception management.

Metaphor:
The shebang line chooses which interpreter runs the script.
In cognition, framing chooses which interpretive model runs incoming data.

Operational translation:
	•	Before action, select the correct interpretive frame.
	•	Before argument, select the proper audience language.
	•	Before code, define the runtime environment.

No seducing the OS.
Just correct interpreter selection.

That’s powerful enough.

